reviews.review_text: the next night Steven Stills showed up and did BLACK  QUEEN

Sounds good to me This tour was a ton of fun, very inspired playing. The boys certainly knew when they had it going on and were firing on all cylinders here.  Listen to the little growls by Jerry during Ramble on rose. Rite out the gate in Richmond during Strangers when Bobby and Brent sing it's gonna be a long long crazy crazy tour....... Also just before U S blues Bobby says relax its a long tour..
 So my point is they came to play in 1983 and am damn glad I was at as many shows I was that year.  
Outstanding fun and Outstanding sound here. 
 To review below Stills played at Brendan Byrne in the spring .both nights. Black Queen 1st night Love the one your with next night. I realize most here know that just pointing it out to other reviewer.   
Thank you for a real good time.
